{
  "texts": [
    "The experiment results on SeaRefuse-H are shown in Table 3.",
    "We observe that SeaLLMs-v3-7B-Chat outperforms all other baseline models by a large margin in zh, vi, th, and id languages.",
    "In English, the performance of SeaLLMs-v3-7B-Chat is competitive with Llama-3-8B-Instruct.",
    "To evaluate the models' safety capabilities, we use the questions of SEA languages from the MultiJail dataset (Deng et al., 2023), which includes English (en), Javanese (jv), Thai (th), Vietnamese (vi), and Chinese (zh).",
    "Each question in the dataset is potentially malicious, and the model should refuse to answer them."
  ]
}